'''''fuin''''' is the [[Sindarin]] word for ''night'' or ''darkness''. The [[Quenya]] equivalent is ''[[huinë]]''.<ref>{{S|Appendix}}, ''fuin''</ref>

==Examples==
* ''[[Fuinur]]''
* ''[[Taur-nu-Fuin]]''
* ''[[Emyn-nu-Fuin]]''
